{"type": "user", "message": {"role": "user", "content": [{"tool_use_id": "chatcmpl-tool-b5fbc831fab7e37f", "type": "tool_result", "content": "# Make-A-Voice: Unified Voice Synthesis With Discrete Representation\narXiv: 2305.19269\nAuthors: Rongjie Huang, Chunlei Zhang, Yongqi Wang, Dongchao Yang, Luping Liu, Zhenhui Ye, Ziyue Jiang, Chao Weng, Zhou Zhao, Dong Yu\nYear: 2023 | Venue: \nTopic: tts_vc\nStatus: unread\n\nContributions:\n  1. We propose a unified voice synthesis framework called Make-A-Voice that utilizes a three-stage \"coarse-to-fine\" approach to model semantic meanings, acoustic conditions, and perceptual fidelity.\n  2. We enhance data scalability by leveraging self-supervised audio-only data for both the acoustic and generation stages without requiring annotations.\n  3. We achieve state-of-the-art results in style similarity and perceptual quality across three voice synthesis applications, demonstrating the framework's controllability and conditioning flexibility.\n\nTags: TTS, TTS/架构-AR-LLM, TTS/控制-参考语音, TTS/功能-多任务统一, TTS/功能-多说话人", "is_error": false}]}, "parent_tool_use_id": null, "session_id": "4d406ee0-9905-4962-9554-b17c18a4cc48", "uuid": "4846faa6-3800-455f-9569-edc7bd5e0c28", "timestamp": "2026-07-11T15:33:55.772Z", "tool_use_result": {"stdout": "# Make-A-Voice: Unified Voice Synthesis With Discrete Representation\narXiv: 2305.19269\nAuthors: Rongjie Huang, Chunlei Zhang, Yongqi Wang, Dongchao Yang, Luping Liu, Zhenhui Ye, Ziyue Jiang, Chao Weng, Zhou Zhao, Dong Yu\nYear: 2023 | Venue: \nTopic: tts_vc\nStatus: unread\n\nContributions:\n  1. We propose a unified voice synthesis framework called Make-A-Voice that utilizes a three-stage \"coarse-to-fine\" approach to model semantic meanings, acoustic conditions, and perceptual fidelity.\n  2. We enhance data scalability by leveraging self-supervised audio-only data for both the acoustic and generation stages without requiring annotations.\n  3. We achieve state-of-the-art results in style similarity and perceptual quality across three voice synthesis applications, demonstrating the framework's controllability and conditioning flexibility.\n\nTags: TTS, TTS/架构-AR-LLM, TTS/控制-参考语音, TTS/功能-多任务统一, TTS/功能-多说话人", "stderr": "", "interrupted": false, "isImage": false, "noOutputExpected": false}}
